| Step | Task                         | Script/Tool Used                    |
| ---- | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| 1    | Create AWS Account           | AWS Website                         |
| 2    | Launch EC2 Instance          | `deploy.sh` + AWS CLI               |
| 3    | Install Java & Git           | `setup.sh`                          |
| 4    | Clone Repo & Deploy App      | `setup.sh`                          |
| 5    | Check App on Port 80         | `test_reachability.sh`              |
| 6    | Stop EC2 Instance            | `stop_instance.sh`                  |
| 7    | Use ENV for Secrets          | `aws configure`                     |
| 8    | Use Stage-Based Config Files | `dev_config.env`, `prod_config.env` |
